OL,3,CBritish tourist attacked by shark is
OL,4,C'aware and able to communicate'
OL,6,FA British tourist who was seriously
OL,7,Finjured in a attack off a Caribbean
OL,8,Fisland is "aware of what is happening
OL,9,Fand can communicate" in intensive
OL,10,Fcare, his wife has said.
OL,12,FPeter Smith, 64, from Berkhamsted,
OL,13,FHertfordshire, was savaged 10 metres
OL,14,Foff the shore near the Starfish Hotel
OL,15,Fin Courland Bay on the north coast of
OL,16,FTobago on Friday morning.
