OL,3,CBritish tourist attacked by shark is
OL,4,C'aware and able to communicate'
OL,6,FHe suffered damage to his left arm and
OL,7,Fleg, puncture wounds to the abdomen
OL,8,Fand injuries to his right hand, the
OL,9,Ffull extent of which are still being
OL,10,Fevaluated after the attack by a bull
OL,11,Fshark.
OL,13,FHe was in a "stable" condition in
OL,14,FScarborough General Hospital in Tobago
OL,15,Fon Sunday after undergoing surgery.
