OL,3,CBritish tourist attacked by shark is
OL,4,C'aware and able to communicate'
OL,6,FHis wife Jo said in a statement
OL,7,Fthrough the BBC: "As of 9am local time
OL,8,Ftoday, Peter is aware of what is
OL,9,Fhappening and is able to communicate a
OL,10,Flittle, although he is still under
OL,11,Fstrong medication."
OL,13,FShe thanked "two friends" who remained
OL,14,Fin the water during the attack to
OL,15,F"battle" the shark, estimated to be
OL,16,F8ft to 10ft long and 2ft wide.
OL,18,FThe couple had been holidaying on the
OL,19,Fisland with friends and were due to
OL,20,Ffly home that day.
