OL,3,CBritish tourist attacked by shark is
OL,4,C'aware and able to communicate'
OL,6,FThe Foreign Office said it was
OL,7,Fsupporting the family.
OL,9,FSeveral beaches and coastal areas were
OL,10,Fclosed and a 10,000 US dollar (#8,000)
OL,11,Fbounty previously offered to anyone
OL,12,Fwho could capture the shark was later
OL,13,Fretracted.
OL,15,FLast year, there were 69 unprovoked
OL,16,Fshark attacks and 22 provoked bites
OL,17,Fworldwide, along with 14 fatalities,
OL,18,Faccording to the Florida-based
OL,19,FInternational Shark Attack File.
